Don’t refer to the chaos that may exist in the office, your loud-mouthed colleagues.
Admit that you have made a mistake and that someone else has had a disadvantage, and eliminate the disadvantage.
Ask how you can make up for your mistake, make up for your failure.
Do you feel at home in the office?
Pants and slippers: comfortable to wear at home, but not in the office!
Don’t wear comfortable clothes when your job allows it.
Don’t be lazy, your colleagues, and honor yourself by going into the office in ordinary clothes – if your job requires it – in a pretty, elegant way.
